{"title_page": "Endless Flowers", "text_new": "{{Infobox album\n| name       = Endless Flowers\n| type       = Studio\n| artist     = [[Crocodiles (band)|Crocodiles]]\n| cover      = Endless Flowers.jpg\n| alt        =\n| released   = {{Start date|2012|06|05}}\n| recorded   =\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Noise pop]]\n| length     = {{Duration|m=41|s=28}}\n| label      = [[French Kiss Records|French Kiss]]\n| producer   =\n| prev_title = [[Sleep Forever]]\n| prev_year  = 2010\n| next_title = [[Crimes of Passion (Crocodiles album)|Crimes of Passion]]\n| next_year  = 2013\n| misc       = {{Singles\n | name        = Endless Flowers\n | type        = Studio\n | single1     = Sunday (Psychic Conversation #9)\n | single1date = April 10, 2012<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/sunday-psychic-conversation/id518222826|title=Sunday (Psychic Conversation #9) - Single|publisher=itunes.apple.com|accessdate=2013-08-22}}</ref>\n | single2     = Endless Flowers\n | single2date = May 8, 2012<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/endless-flowers-single/id521022229|title=Endless Flowers - Single|publisher=itunes.apple.com|accessdate=2013-08-22}}</ref>\n}}\n}}\n\n{{Album ratings\n| MC = 66/100<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/endless-flowers/crocodiles|title=Endless Flowers Reviews|publisher=Metacritic.com|accessdate=2013-08-22}}</ref>\n| rev1 = ''[[This Is Fake DIY]]''\n| rev1Score = 9/10<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thisisfakediy.co.uk/articles/albums/crocodiles-endless-flowers/|title=Crocodiles - Endless Flowers|publisher=ThisIsFakeDIY.co.uk|last=Lucas|first=Kosta|accessdate=2013-08-22}}</ref>\n| rev2 = [[AllMusic]]\n| rev2Score = {{Rating|3.5|5}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/endless-flowers-mw0002322234|title=Endless Flowers - Crocodiles|publisher=Allmusic.com|last=Wilkinson|first=James|accessdate=2013-08-22}}</ref>\n| rev3 = ''[[musicOMH]]''\n| rev3Score = {{Rating|4|5}}<ref>{{cite web|url=