agano Parceiro Ladies|Ohara JaSRA L.S.C.]]||21||7||4||10||26||39|| -13||'''25'''||\n|-\n|6||align=\"left\"|[[Bunnys Kyoto S.C.]]||21||4||5||12||16||46|| -30||'''17'''||\n|-\n|7||align=\"left\"|[[Je Vrille Kagoshima]]||21||5||2||14||22||58|| -36||'''17'''||\n|-\n|8||align=\"left\"|[[Mashiki Renaissance Kumamoto F.C.|Renaissance Kumamoto F.C.]]||21||1||2||18||12||150|| -138||'''5'''||\n|}\n\n*Best Player: [[Yoshie Kasazaki]], AS Elfen Sayama F.C.\n\n==Promotion/Relegation Series==\n\n===Division 1 Promotion/Relegation Series===\n\n{{footballbox\n|date=2009-11-08\n|time=13:00\n|team1=[[Speranza F.C. Osaka-Takatsuki|Speranza F.C. Takatsuki]]\n|score= 0 - 3\n|report=\n|team2=[[Fukuoka J. Anclas]]\n|stadium=[[Takatsuki Hagitani Soccer Stadium]]\n}}\n----\n{{footballbox\n|date=2009-11-15\n|time=14:00\n|team1=[[Fukuoka J. Anclas]]\n|score= 0 - 1\n|report=\n|team2=[[Speranza F.C. Osaka-Takatsuki|Speranza F.C. Takatsuki]]\n|stadium=[[Ogoori, Fukuoka]]\n}}\n\n*''Fukuoka J. Anclas'' Promoted for Division 1 in [[2010 L. League|2010 Season]].\n*''Speranza F.C. Takatsuki'' Relegated to Division 2 in 2010 Season.\n\n===Division 2 Promotion Series===\n\n====BLOCK A====\n{{footballbox\n|date=2009-11-21\n|time=11:00\n|team1=[[Shizuoka Sangyo University Iwata Bonita|Shizuoka Sangyo University Iwata Ladies]]\n|score= 0 - 3\n|report=\n|team2=[[Nippon Sport Science University L.S.C.]]\n|stadium=[[Susono, Shizuoka]]\n}}\n----\n{{footballbox\n|date=2009-11-21\n|time=11:00\n|team1=[[Hoyo Sukarabu F.C.]]\n|score= 0 - 7\n|report=\n|team2=[[JFA Academy Fukushima L.F.C.]]\n|stadium=[[Susono, Shizuoka]]\n}}\n----\n{{footballbox\n|date=2009-11-22\n|time=11:00\n|team1=[[JFA Academy Fukushima L.F.C.]]\n|score= 5 - 1\n|report=\n|team2=[[Shizuoka Sangyo University Iwata Bonita|Shizuoka Sangyo University Iwata Ladies]]\n|stadium=[[Susono, Shizuoka]]\n}}\n----\n{{footballbox\n|date=2009-11-22\n|time=11:00\n|team1=[[Hoyo Sukarabu F.C.]]\n|score= 0 - 3\n|report=\n|team2=[[Nippon Sport Science University L